Robert Andrews (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Andrews_(actor) 0 Robert Tobias "Bobbie" Andrews (20 February 1895 – 17 January 1976) born Reginald Frank Andrews, was a British stage actor. He also briefly appeared in films. Robert_Tobias_"_Bobbie_"_Andrews ( 20_February_1895 – 17_January_1976 ) born Reginald_Frank_Andrews , was a_British_stage_actor . He also briefly appeared in films .
